                  "revisionId": 2784131,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "In most cases, this mod will lower average damage. As such, it is not recommended for any gun other than those with a high critical hit rate (such as the Magnus ) and only with particular mod setups already in place."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Hollow Point",
                  "pageId": 233564,
                  "revisionId": 2784131,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "It is worth noting that modifications to the same stat are additive and as a result Hollow Point's damage penalty is less substantial when placed on a gun already modified with a high-ranking Hornet Strike . In fact, a gun with a maxed rank copy of Hornet Strike will drop from 320% damage per shot to 305% damage per shot, which is slightly less than an effective damage drop of 5%."
                }
              }
